in exchange for your sight.

75
00:05:45,370 --> 00:05:48,250
Even if I can never see your face again,

76
00:05:46,670 --> 00:05:49,600
♫Dancing in silk robes, beautifully adorned♫

77
00:05:49,530 --> 00:05:51,370
I am willing to do this.

