80
00:06:10,890 --> 00:06:12,570
It's indeed my one-sided love.

81
00:06:14,570 --> 00:06:16,570
Ying, from beginning to end,

82
00:06:18,010 --> 00:06:19,650
has always loved Su Wuyang.

83
00:06:22,130 --> 00:06:24,380
There was never a place for me in her heart.

84
00:06:25,280 --> 00:06:27,000
Never.

85
00:06:29,250 --> 00:06:30,410
But it doesn't matter.

86
00:06:33,270 --> 00:06:34,290
Ying,

87
00:06:35,930 --> 00:06:38,050
I promised to make you happy,

88
00:06:39,610 --> 00:06:41,570
and I will keep my word.
